      "anchor_proposed": {
        "vr_id": 54636,
        "reference": "Luk 5:22",
        "strongs": "G1260",
        "translit": "dialogizomai",
        "anchor_rationale": "'And immediately Jesus, perceiving in his spirit that they thus questioned within themselves, said to them, Why do you question these things in your hearts?' The phenomenon at its clearest: inner deliberative reasoning (dialogizomai) located explicitly in the heart, perceived by Jesus in his spirit, named and challenged. The verse makes the inner activity, its location, and its perceptibility to Christ all explicit simultaneously."
      }
